headline: KeyBank Provides $19.5 Million of Financing for Affordable Senior Housing in Florida
summary: CLEVELAND, OH / ACCESS Newswire / August 28, 2025 / KeyBank Community Development Lending and Investment (CDLI) provided a $13 million construction loan to finance the new construction of Hawthorne Heights, an 86-unit affordable senior housing project ...
